<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA99">
<l>toṭṭa paṭaiyeṭṭun tōlāta veṉṟiyā</l>
<l>ṉaṭṭa puyakarattā ṉannāṉṟu – kuṭṭattuk</l>
<l>kōṇmutalai tuñcak kuṟitteṟinta cakkarattāṉ</l>
<l>ṟāṇmutalē naṅkaṭkuc cārvu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The victorious one whose eight  weapons, which he grasps, are unvanquished,</l>
<l>the one with eight arms [and] hands , the one with the discus that he threw</l>
<l>at that time, aiming at the murderous crocodile when it slept in the pond,</l>
<l>at [his] feet [there is] refuge for us.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
